{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UfL9LvVKdQqTbiNz7UAk4A","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Written to `tools/title-loop/docs/22-480d364/feedback.md`.\n\n**8 patterns found, grouped by root cause:**\n\n1. **OCR corruption accepted verbatim** (11) — Correct line found but `1→l`, `0→O`, `¡→i` etc. passed through unchanged. Needs normalization post-extraction.\n\n2. **Section/page header chosen over title** (6) — Lines like `Page 102 - SOUPS & BROTHS` or `FISH & SEAFOOD` scored higher than the actual recipe title below them.\n\n3. **Previous-page overflow at file start** (2) — File opens with `PREVIOUS RECIPE OVERFLOW:` fragment; extractor takes it as the title.\n\n4. **Multi-part title truncated** (4) — Titles with ` : ` or ` + ` connectors (dual-recipe pages) get shortened to one half.\n\n5. **Multi-line title not joined** (4) — Title spread across 2–3 short lines (`ROSEMARY` / `FOCACCIA` / `BREAD`); extractor picks one fragment or misses entirely.\n\n6. **\"(OCR CORRUPTION: …)\" marker causes fallthrough** (5) — Template artifact: the annotation line causes the extractor to reject the valid title above it and scrape garbage from deep in the file.\n\n7. **Recipe section header returned instead of title** (7) — Short/single-word titles lose to later section headings (`PASTA MAKOWA:`, `Roasting:`, `Chocolate sauce:`).\n\n8. **Title absent from file** (1) — Ingredients start on line 1; no title present; extractor returns a fallback phrase.\n\nHighest-priority fixes: #1 (normalization), #2 (section/page header skip), #7 (short-title scoring), #5 (multi-line joining) — all four likely affect real files too."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3166,"cache_read_input_tokens":39912,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3166},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"53735f72-1291-447c-9abf-b077c22e3b1b","uuid":"50b33509-2bbf-4d3e-a9e0-76b13fe9ee1f"}
